snippet.title: Dragon Age Legends - Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Before the launch of Dragon Age II, return to Thedas in Dragon Age Legends on Facebook.  Take down demons and darkspawn with your friends in this action-packed, free online RPG.  Be Legendary! Play here now: http://bit.ly/h6xtk7
